   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Furnish a school for 75 disabled children in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our work is going to be vital and life changing for the disabled children in our community. We have the vision &amp; passion to provide for these children&apos;s future education. Our classrooms will give life changing access to education for disabled children.   We have to furnish &amp; equip 3 classrooms. Every child has the right to learn despite disability, sadly our communities are impoverished. Funds for special needs children are rarely considered. We will improve the learning &amp; vitally, the teaching.</narrative>
  </description>
